&lt;h2>Overview&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="overview">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#overview" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>A web application that represents a &lt;strong>&lt;a href="https://beets.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">beets&lt;/a>&lt;/strong> music library as an &lt;strong>interactive constellation&lt;/strong>. Each star is an album or artist, and the links between them illustrate relationships (genres, years, similarities).&lt;/p>
&lt;p>A poetic, visual way to explore your music collection.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2>Features&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="features">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#features" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Connect to a beets library (via the beets web API)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>SVG/Canvas constellation graph representation&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Interactive navigation (zoom, pan, select)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Filter by genre, decade, artist&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2>Stack&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="stack">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#stack" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>TypeScript&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Visualisation: D3.js or Canvas&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Backend: beets API&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
